libdiskimage
============

This is libdiskimage, a cross-platform library written in C++ for accessing
hard and floppy disk drive images.

For more information, take a look at the included man pages.
  
For generic installation instructions, see file 'INSTALL'.

If you make a binary distribution, include a pointer to the official
distribution site:

	http://code.google.com/p/libdiskimage

The latest version can always be found there.

Mail suggestions and bug reports to <mressl@umich.edu>.
